    public class NormGroupCombination
extends java.util.HashMap<NormCompliance,java.util.HashMap<NormCompliance,NormGroup>>
    A class that contains the four combinations of compliance of a pair of norms. That is, Fulfilment/Fulfilment, Fulfilment/Infringement, Infringement/Fulfilment and Infringement/Infringement
    Author:
    "Javier Morales (jmorales@iiia.csic.es)"
